Safety and activity of microRNA-loaded minicells in patients with recurrent 
malignant pleural mesothelioma: a first-in-man, phase 1, open-label, 
dose-escalation study.

van Zandwijk N(1), Pavlakis N(2), Kao SC(3), Linton A(4), Boyer MJ(5), Clarke 
S(2), Huynh Y(6), Chrzanowska A(6), Fulham MJ(7), Bailey DL(8), Cooper WA(9), 
